'''Shon Weissman''' ({{lang-he|שון וייסמן}}; born 14 February 1996) is an [[Israel]]i [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a Forward for the Austrian club [[Wolfsberger AC]].

==Honours==
*'''[[Liga Leumit]]'''
**'''Winner (1):''' 2016-17

